data.description: Open house today (March 3rd) 12:00-5:00 PM. Are you a VA buyer looking for an assumable mortgage?! This home has a 2.25% assumable loan with a balance of $710,000! This stunning single-family residence offers the perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and convenience. Located in the prestigious Hoakalei neighborhood, this home boasts a prime position adjacent to the Hoakalei Country Club golf course, providing breathtaking views and access to pristine greens. Enjoy the nearby Wai Kai Lagoon, offering a wave pool, upscale dining, bars, and water sports. Residents also benefit from a state-of-the-art community center with a pool, jacuzzi, tennis court, and event space. Step into your own outdoor oasis with a spacious backyard featuring mature landscaping and a sprinkler system. With four bedrooms, including a luxurious primary suite, and two and a half baths, this meticulously designed home offers approximately 1,688 square feet of generous living space. The two-car garage provides convenience and additional storage. Embrace the laid-back lifestyle of Hawaii with easy access to beaches and the Ka Makana Alii mall. Schedule your private showing today!
